<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container mb-4 p-4">
      <div class="content mb-4 p-4">
        <h1 class="m-4 color-theme">Contact us</h1>
        <p>
          If you have any concerns or inquiries, feel free to reach out to us.
          Our dedicated team is here to assist you. You can contact us through
          the following channels:
        </p>

        <h2>Visit Our Offices:</h2>
        <p>
          Get insights into how our agents serve food at different places by
          visiting our offices:
        </p>
        <address>
          <p>Kondhwa Office:</p>
          <p>Address: XYZ Nagar, Kondhwa, Pune</p>
        </address>
        <address>
          <p>Bibwewadi Office:</p>
          <p>Address: XYZ Vihar, Bibwewadi, Pune</p>
        </address>

        <h2>Email Us:</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Aishwarya Talebailkar:
            <a href="mailto:annaseva@vit.edu">mailto:annaseva@vit.edu</a>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          We value your suggestions and feedback. Feel free to email us. We
          appreciate your input and strive to continually improve our services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-container">
        <h2>Contact Form</h2>
        <form>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="firstName">First Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="lastName">Last Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
